{"tid":2208925,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陸頌雄: 得一名外籍非常任法官辭任　反映餘下在任13名法官向本港司法制度投下信心一票","createTime":"2020-09-19T09:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T09:46:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cd63cf76737eb319e6f73f54e06b17fe0f91daaa","tid":2208925,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:28:42.000Z","msg":"對於施覺民的離任，英國保守黨前黨魁施志安（Iain Duncan Smith）向外媒表示，擔心法官未來需要為政權進行掩飾，又指香港目前的情況是把正直的人置於無法忍受的制度中，認為這是英國或澳洲等司法獨立的地方不會出現的問題。另一方面，也有外媒引述本港大律師消息指，相信有其他資深法官亦正為自己的未來打算，暗示將會有其他法官離職的消息出現。<br />\n<br />\n議員陸頌雄指施覺民辭任一事只是有人「辭官歸故里」，不明白為何會有人把事件放大，甚至把事件與司法不公掛鈎。陸反指，本港原有14名外籍非常任法官，若套用上述邏輯推論，不就是反映餘下在任的13名法官向本港司法制度投下信心一票。<br />\n<br />\n陸強調本港司法制度一直名列世界前茅，甚在排在英國和美國之上，不認為一定要任用洋法官，才能肯定本港的司法制度。在陸看來，即使沒有洋法官，本港亦能維持公平公正，又指大部分外國國家都沒有任用外籍法官的制度，認為若洋法官不滿本港現況，港府可隨着他們的自然流失而讓本地人才取締。"},{"pid":"be33b89710aacea954e0dd118d1432018f8fa1f6","tid":2208925,"uid":65790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:29:41.000Z","msg":"又係呢條鄉下佬，等睇其他人辭任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4f145bd37598309027f4631a59121f98764163","tid":2208925,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"be33b89710aacea954e0dd118d1432018f8fa1f6","tid":2208925,"uid":65790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:29:41.000Z","msg":"又係呢條鄉下佬，等睇其他人辭任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:31:57.000Z","msg":"港版國安法陰霾下，不少國家提醒國民來港要小心被捕，甚至有被引渡回內地的風險，早前也有報道指外籍法官因國籍問題不獲指派處理國安法案件。早前終審法院非常任法官韋彥德（The Right Honourable Lord Reed of Allermuir）披露，兩個來自英國最高法院的香港終審法院非常任法官席位，今年只剩一個，而且未獲編排審理香港案件。韋彥德指，英國最高法院法官能否繼續為香港服務，要視乎香港是否仍能維持司法獨立。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200919/SFXBBORYDBE4ZJZMRAOJCNWDMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200919%2FSFXBBORYDBE4ZJZMRAOJCNWDMQ%2F&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCpFs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=798cbcfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200919%2FSFXBBORYDBE4ZJZMRAOJCNWDMQ%2F&h=11f2941e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200919/SFXBBORYDBE4ZJZMRAOJCNWDMQ/</a>"},{"pid":"f183c5b87500b1131435763776d08b47c9cd20cf","tid":2208925,"uid":37232,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:33:11.000Z","msg":"得百幾萬參加驗測=5百萬人反對驗測"},{"pid":"9e20c7f2d759cdcf1979cdb7b521fd1be619df25","tid":2208925,"uid":123774,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:33:39.000Z","msg":"得178萬參與檢<br />\n當2成被迫參與嘅打工仔<br />\n即係最起碼500萬人對中央不信任"},{"pid":"2a5e27916742589af6f22fc6b95de11588234e12","tid":2208925,"uid":133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e20c7f2d759cdcf1979cdb7b521fd1be619df25","tid":2208925,"uid":123774,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:33:39.000Z","msg":"得178萬參與檢<br />\n當2成被迫參與嘅打工仔<br />\n即係最起碼500萬人對中央不信任"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feea386b20ae486a98f63c929591e73ddf6168dd","tid":2208925,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:37:28.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲非黑即白論調<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2e49f7d0ce82364a84010c534d64d74876b2c3","tid":2208925,"uid":268547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:38:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">留名睇總辭</span>"},{"pid":"b55a414d1099e741f3b5218b68cad69e0a440690","tid":2208925,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:41:54.000Z","msg":"泛民見到呢啲撚人鳩up 仲好意思講接受委任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721d0c80bd3b4064f74d1184337e32caaee3e4c2","tid":2208925,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:45:08.000Z","msg":"得170萬人做武肺檢測, 證明580萬反對政府"},{"pid":"07652886182da5e662eafec60882d842bd240fed","tid":2208925,"uid":342855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:46:35.000Z","msg":"Korea Fish：有130萬韓粉！"},{"pid":"06657e29691de1524e6957df5aa4a2106d99ff74","tid":2208925,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:46:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/australian-james-spigelman-resigns-as-judge-of-hong-kong-appeals-court-over-new-national-security-law\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Flanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Faustralian-james-spigelman-resigns-as-judge-of-hong-kong-appeals-court-over-new-national-security-law&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCpFs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=af27720a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/australian-james-spigelman-resigns-as-judge-of-hong-kong-appeals-court-over-new-national-security-law</a><br />\n施覺民的離職引起揣測其他外籍法官是否都會辭職。不過，范禮全向澳洲廣播公司表示，他會繼續其職務。<br />\n<br />\n范禮全說：「我極其讚賞那法院的首席法官和其他常任法官，以及讚賞他們致力維持司法獨立。我繼續在任，反映我支持他們的努力，以及我信任他們能勝任。否則我便不會繼續做。」"},{"pid":"367c1d868c26d12a308f83c146aa14e82e2c68e7","tid":2208925,"uid":108213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:46:57.000Z","msg":"得百幾萬全民檢查<br />\n反映全港600萬人反777反共  反國安法"}]}